wing homes:", "Date First Owner Address", "Mrs. Adeline Belcher 1898 305 18th Street", "W. H. Stephens 1892 112 Forest Avenue", "Mrs. Charlotte Saal 1889 316 8th Street", "Christian Church Christian Church 1896", "Dr. Andrew Hart 649 Lighthouse 1894 ...............................................................................", "Can-oll Jeanne GingTas has agreed to be Chairperson of Dosents. She", "coordinates the hosts and hostesses who greet visitors at Ketchum's Barn on", "Saturdays from 1-4 p.m. If you are able to donate three hours of your time on", "Saturday afternoon please contact Carroll at 372-3700. a", "Currently on exhibit at Ketchum' s Barn is \"nie Chautauqua Connection,\"", "centering around clothing loaned to the Heritage Society by the Goldsworthy", "sisters, whose mother and aunt wore the garments to Chautauqua meetings. Also", "display are many photos not seen before. Stop in Saturdays from 1 :00 to on", "4:00 p.m. 'nlis exhibit will continue until sometime in November."], "bbox": [[0.066622, 0.059777, 0.07771200000000002, 0.057036], [0.497899, 0.057025, 0.09386300000000003, 0.060521], [0.170588, 0.039558, 0.780427, 0.083386], [0.292639, 0.153697, 0.4356300000000001, 0.019092], [0.750286, 0.188239, 0.15577599999999991, 0.017428], [0.192134, 0.202764, -0.010941000000000006, 0.017428], [0.192202, 0.222431, 0.7152189999999999, 0.017428], [0.143025, 0.243524, 0.7646139999999999, 0.017428], [0.143042, 0.263773, 0.763201, 0.017428], [0.143462, 0.284296, 0.763166, 0.017428], [0.142857, 0.304818, 0.762961, 0.017428], [0.143378, 0.325626, 0.21217599999999998, 0.017428], [0.192555, 0.345863, 0.7139159999999999, 0.017428], [0.143378, 0.366659, 0.763091, 0.017428], [0.144185, 0.386909, 0.763282, 0.017428], [0.143042, 0.407419, 0.262247, 0.017428], [0.193681, 0.427669, 0.7138490000000001, 0.017428], [0.143664, 0.448761, 0.732096, 0.017428], [0.192202, 0.469284, 0.715019, 0.017428], [0.144403, 0.490091, 0.762807, 0.017428], [0.143647, 0.510329, 0.762359, 0.01